1. *Uvo* mi je jako osetljivo na hladnoću. (My *ear* is very sensitive to cold.)
2. Danas sam bila kod doktora zbog bola u *uvu*. (Today I went to the doctor because of ear pain.)
3. Zalutala mi je dlaka u *uvo* i ne mogu je izvaditi. (A hair got stuck in my *ear* and I can't get it out.)
4. *Uvo* telefona je prljavo, treba da ga očistim. (The *receiver* of the phone is dirty, I need to clean it.)
5. *Uvo* u ljudskom telu ima važnu ulogu u održavanju ravnoteže. (The *inner ear* in the human body has an important role in maintaining balance.)
6. *Uvo* je jedan od pet osnovnih čula. (Hearing is one of the five basic senses.)
7. Nismo se čuli od juče, javi mi se kad god stigneš na *uvo*. (We haven't talked since yesterday, call me whenever you get a chance *to answer the phone*.)
8. *Uvo* žita se koristi za dobijanje brašna. (The *ear* of wheat is used to make flour.)